    .duration
      2013 - 2007 (6 years)
    %p.job-description
      While at OHSU, I built a barcode label based database for organism inventory and lineage tracking using the Filemaker Pro database application. I maintained multiple microscopes and the software packages to operate them. I developed software tools in Python for manipulating and visualizing RNA and DNA sequences. I maintained and programmed aquaria monitoring and alarm systems. I was involved in hiring process and decisions and had some managerial oversight over multiple facility employees.

